FBIS3-12425 "drnes040_l_94011" FBIS-NES-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Mar 1994 ISRAEL Automatic Weapons of Extremist Settlers To Be Seized TA2802165494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1600 GMT 28 Feb 94 TA2802165494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] The police minister has ordered the confiscation of the automatic weapons of extremist settlers in Judaea and Samaria, but let them keep their personal weapons, such as guns. He also ordered the police commissioner to release all the Israeli Arabs who were arrested during demonstrations in the last few days if they are not suspected of having hit policemen or damaged property.
